;\"><strong>wait, <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果confirm 有11.24區議會選舉,強烈建議48小時前 無任何行動,以防POPO捉人呃票</strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:41:43.000Z","msg":"呢個有考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2c7f97c4e6b405a4ed1816f39881c30cd9a57e","tid":1727481,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:58:40.000Z","msg":"認受性低 活動有舉行空間/未是時候, 但是神燈燒生出招, 大家記得去做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9620dabe0f8d034184276fd376a4e1fe65745b5","tid":1727481,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6e93dc750036380c2a5ebfca953aa1f487e7e03","tid":1727481,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:46:07.000Z","msg":"[突發] V小隊預告行動升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/exdugS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/exdugS</a><br />\n<br />\n個人立場：不反對區選, 但希望在於人民, 並非選票(幾十萬未成年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)！<br />\n<br />\n人口分佈<br />\n新界:九龍:港島 ~<span style=\"color: red;\"> 4:2:1</span><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n規劃署今日（六月八日）發表載列2018年至2026年香港人口分布最新推算數字的「人口分布推算2018－2026」報告書。推算新界及九龍的人口，在2016年至2026年期間，會分別增加441600人及140200人，在2026年其人口會分別達到428萬人及238萬人，而同期間香港島的人口，則由125萬逐漸減少至116萬。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新界</span></strong><br />\n1. 屯門  (參考過往遊行)<br />\n2. 沙田  (參考過往遊行)<br />\n3. 大埔  (參考過往遊行) <br />\n4. 上水  (參考過往遊行)<br />\n5. 荃葵青  (參考過往遊行)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">九龍</span></strong><br />\n6. 油尖旺  (參考過往遊行)<br />\n<del>7. 黃大仙</del><span style=\"color: red;\"> (可以拼合埋觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />達成九之數, 咒死中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</span><br />\n8. 觀塘 (參考過往遊行)<br />\n9. TKO  (參考過往遊行)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">港島</span></strong><br />\n10. 港島  (參考過往遊行)<br />\n<br />\n[破局] 令藍絲老解收皮、黑警精神更崩潰，搞多次超多人既大型活動就得<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1727350\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1727350</a><br />\n<br />\nBtw 終於明點解港島不利港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n抄班神鬼風水撚口吻講<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">九</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">龍</span></strong>克撚死中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">九</span></strong>代表亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>龍</strong></span>代表天命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">11.23 反解放軍聯合陣線！「逢九必亂」！九陣遊行！</span></span></strong><br />\n有冇得諗？下星期六11月23日搞遊行, 呢九個區包納曬<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>港九新界</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有得諗, 照舊遊行路線, 落街就示威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇得諗, 班POPO唔會比你地和平集結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推到民陣申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:07:46.000Z","msg":"鍾意玩風水既<br />\n可以加入大鵬金翅鳥元素 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eeb7617d0d9717926ea21d2663b1226b76a20d4","tid":1727481,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:09:20.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"f5cb4cc81d51e179ae084c314c520c7b7b1ca9aa","tid":1727481,"uid":80437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:11:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">浸大RB一定一定一定唔可以SET，因為如果老解再出，林奠會好難做！因為第一次當無通知你，如果再出，林奠會解釋唔到。所以如果最後老解唔出的話，老解同雜種會好無面！<br />\n我地唔可以俾領導人難做的！一定唔可以再去果到SET RB!!!!!大家説對不對！？<